                "description": {
                    "value": "<p data-visibility=\"gm\"><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature moves within 10 feet of the platform;</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> All creatures within 10 feet of the platform must each attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-traits=\"arcane,electricity,evocation,magical,trap\" data-pf2-label=\"Magnetic Drag DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"23\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span> save. Creatures who are wearing metal armor or are made of metal suffer a -2 circumstance penalty to this save.</p>\n<div data-visibility=\"gm\">\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is dragged 5 feet toward the platform.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is dragged onto the platform, which is quickly raised on chains 30 feet into the air. The creature is then struck by lightning for [[/r 4d8+14 #electricity]]{4d8+14 electricity damage}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but the creature is also knocked @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Prone]{Prone} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Restrained]{Restrained} on the platform (Escape DC 20).</p>\n</div>"
